screen_desc:
The screenshot shows a mobile interface for searching an address. At the top, the time is displayed as 11:25 AM, and there are various status icons for notifications, Bluetooth, VPN, signal strength, and battery level. Below that, there is a search bar with the text "Washington Hilton" entered and a clear button (X) on the right side. Three search results are displayed:

1. 17 Washington Street, Hilton SA 5033, Australia
2. 18A Washington Street, Hilton SA 5033, Australia
3. 6 Washington Street, Hilton SA 5033, Australia

At the bottom of the screen, there is a keyboard with a background image of a night sky and a tent. The keyboard layout includes numbers, letters, and various function keys. The keyboard is labeled "Laban Key."
